910302002.content: Wanna know the secret to winning a snowball fight?

910302003.content: In a snowball fight, you just ball up snow in your hands and throw it. Easy, right?

910302004.content: However, there's more to it than just chucking a snowball!

910302005.content: You have to hit your opponent with the snowballs, sure, but you also have to dodge the ones they throw at you.

910302006.content: Not only that, you also need a steady supply of snowballs on hand!

910302007.content: During our warmup just there, you hit me once and I hit you three times.

910302008.content: Looking back, I think I was out of "ammo" each time you hit me.

910302009.content: Hehe, I do make "snow ammo" pretty quickly!

910302010.content: But you're really good at dodging, Administrator! A lot of my snowballs didn't even hit you.

910302011.content: Hm... Lemme think... Why don't we try it this way next!

910302012.content: I'll cover the "ammo" side of things, and you'll cover me!

910302013.content: If I'm confident about anything, it's my speed.

910302014.content: Great! Then while they're making the "ammo," we'll switch and I'll cover you.

910302015.content: Wait... Won't you have the advantage if you're throwing?

910302016.content: Huh? You mean, like, I'd use Divine Power to throw the snowballs?

910302018.content: I'll rely purely on my strength to fight with you until the bitter end!

910302019.content: Got it. I'll do my best too then.

910302021.content: Lastly, I'd just like to say...

910302022.content: Whether we win or lose, it's an honor fighting with you.

910302023.content: Let's make as many snowballs as we can!
